OL,3,CThree men sentenced to life in prison
OL,4,Cfor murder of Ian Ogle
OL,6,FThree men have been found guilty of
OL,7,Fthe murder of Ian Ogle in Belfast in
OL,8,F2019. All three have been sentenced to
OL,9,Flife in prison.
OL,11,FDelivering his verdict in the non-jury
OL,12,Ftrial at Belfast Crown Court, Mr
OL,13,FJustice McFarland said he was
OL,14,Fsatisfied that Glenn Rainey, 38,
OL,15,FWalter Ervine, 43, and 41-year-old
OL,16,FRobert Spiers were part of a group of
OL,17,Ffive men who had attacked Mr Ogle.
OL,19,FThere were cheers from the Ogle family
OL,20,Fwhen the verdict was announced.
