OL,6,FThe family of Ian Ogle expressed
OL,7,Frelief at the end of a "long,
OL,8,Fdifficult process" after three men
OL,9,Fwere found guilty of his murder in
OL,10,FBelfast.
OL,12,FThey also called for a "serious look"
OL,13,Fat the judicial system in Northern
OL,14,FIreland and described as "unfair" how
OL,15,Flong victims have to wait for a trial
OL,16,Fin the region compared with the rest
OL,17,Fof the UK.
