OL,3,CThree men sentenced to life in prison
OL,4,Cfor murder of Ian Ogle
OL,6,FMr Ogle was 45 when he was beaten and
OL,7,Fstabbed 11 times just yards from his
OL,8,FCluan Place home in the east of the
OL,9,Fcity in January 2019.
OL,11,FDelivering his verdict in the non-jury
OL,12,Ftrial, Mr Justice McFarland said he
OL,13,Fwas satisfied that Glenn Rainey, 38,
OL,14,Ffrom Ballyhalbert Caravan Park, Walter
OL,15,FErvine, 43, from Litchfield Street in
OL,16,FBelfast, and Robert Spiers, 41, from
OL,17,FMillars Park in Dundonald, were part
OL,18,Fof a group of five men who had carried
OL,19,Fout the attack.
