OL,6,FThe judge told the three men the only
OL,7,Fsentence he could hand down was life
OL,8,Fimprisonment.
OL,10,FThe three defendants showed no emotion
OL,11,Fas the verdicts were read.
OL,13,FThere were emotional scenes outside
OL,14,Fcourt as Mr Ogle's family gathered
OL,15,Ftogether to say the Lord's Prayer.
