OL,3,CThree men sentenced to life in prison
OL,4,Cfor murder of Ian Ogle
OL,6,FMr Ogle's daughter Toni Johnston
OL,7,Fthanked all those who supported the
OL,8,Ffamily since her father's murder in
OL,9,F2019, the detectives involved in the
OL,10,Finvestigation and the judge for
OL,11,Fbringing the case to a successful
OL,12,Fconclusion, describing a "difficult
OL,13,Fprocess".
OL,15,F"As anyone who has witnessed the trial
OL,16,Fand heard the facts and evidence will
OL,17,Fknow, it was a very complex one," she
OL,18,Fsaid.
