OL,3,CThree men sentenced to life in prison
OL,4,Cfor murder of Ian Ogle
OL,6,F"It has taken almost six years to get
OL,7,Fto this moment and that has been a
OL,8,Fparticularly difficult experience.
OL,10,F"The judicial system in Northern
OL,11,FIreland needs serious change,
OL,12,Fparticularly when a crime of this
OL,13,Fseriousness has been committed.
OL,15,F"We believe it is unfair that victims
OL,16,Fand witnesses in Northern Ireland have
OL,17,Fto wait so long to go through this
OL,18,Fprocess and see justice delivered.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@AOU
