OL,4,Cfor murder of Ian Ogle
OL,6,F"I also want to emphasise that after
OL,7,Fwaiting so long for a trial to take
OL,8,Fplace, it took a further 10 months for
OL,9,Fit to be completed.
OL,11,F"In the meantime, those charged with
OL,12,Fmurder and assisting offences lived in
OL,13,Four community yards from where the
OL,14,Fcrime took place.
OL,16,F"They were also yards from the murder
OL,17,Fvictim's family.
