OL,4,Cfor murder of Ian Ogle
OL,6,F"The length of the wait put
OL,7,Findefensible strains on the people
OL,8,Fdirectly involved in the trial as well
OL,9,Fas having a damaging effect on the
OL,10,Fwider community.
OL,12,F"In Northern Ireland, I believe we
OL,13,Fshould have some serious conversations
OL,14,Fabout why our trial process takes so
OL,15,Fmuch longer than in the rest of the
OL,16,FUK."
